title: The First Ever Radio Hour 10/17/22
itunes:title: The First Ever Radio Hour 10/17/22
description:
On this weeks radio hour you’ll hear some of great new music from Militarie Gun, Tigers Jaw, Gillian Carter, Fleshwater, Turnover, Plains, Creeks, Death Cab For Cutie and more!

Subscribe to the PATREON and receive a brand new radio hour every Sunday! Thats two additional episodes a month AND you get them a day early! You'll also see a complete list of songs played on this episode.

Follow the show on Instagram and Twitter!
